author: Disney
description:
Fun fact: The scene in TRON: ARES of Eve Kim, played by Greta Lee, and godmother of AI Dr. Fei Fei Li was actually filmed on the real TED stage at the TED2024 Conference in Vancouver. Hear from Lee as she reflects on her time at TED what it was like to work with Dr. Li in this exclusive clip.

Experience Tron: Ares now playing in theaters and IMAX. Get tickets now.
